quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,26,"Nokorε sε, Yε’bͻͻ onipa fri nεteε a awoͻ a εnee wͻ mu a efri atεkyε a yanwene mu"
  15,27,Ɛna Jinn no nso Yedii kan bͻͻ no fri ogya kεterεma mu (ansa na yεrebͻ onipa)
  15,28,"Kae εberε a wo Wura Nyankopͻn ka kyerεε Soro abͻfoͻ no sε: “Merebεbͻ onipa afri nεteε a awoͻ a εnee wͻ mu a efri atεkyε a yanwene mu”"
  15,29,"“Enti sε Menwene no pεpεεpε wie na Mehome Mehonhom gu ne mu a, monfa moho nkͻ fͻm na monfa moanim mmutu fͻm ma no"
  15,30,Enti Soro abͻfoͻ no nyinaa bͻͻ mu de wͻn anim butuu fͻm (brεε wͻn ho ase) maa (Adam)
  15,31,"Gyesε Ibliis, wampene sε ͻbεka wͻn a wͻ’de wͻn anim butuu fͻm (brεε wͻn ho aseε) no ho"
  15,32,"Nyankopͻn kaa sε: “Ibliis, εdeεn na εha woͻ a w’annka wͻn a wͻ’de wͻn anim butuu fͻm no ho"
  15,33,"(Ibliis) kaa sε: “Menyε obi a mede m’anim bebutu fͻm ama onipa a Wobͻͻ no fri nεteε a awoͻ a εnee wͻ mu a efri atεkyε a yanwene mu”"
  15,34,"Onyankopͻn kaa sε: “Ɛneε fri ha kͻ, nokorε sε, yato wo atwene (afri Nyankopͻn ahummͻborͻ no mu)"
  15,35,"Nokorε sε, Onyankopͻn nnomee wͻ woso kͻpem Akatua Da no"
  15,36,"Ɔkaa sε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn, εneε na mame berε (anaasε enku me) kosi Da a yεbenyane awufoͻ no“"
  15,37,"Onyankopͻn kaa sε: “Woka wͻn a yama wͻn εberε no ho"
  15,38,Kͻpem Dͻnhwere no a yenim“
  15,39,"(Ibliis) kaa sε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn, sεdeε W’ama me ayera yi deε, nokorε sε, mεma (bͻne) ayε wͻn fε wͻ asaase so, na m’ayera wͻn nyinaa"
  15,40,Gyesε Wonkoa a wͻ’di nokorε a wͻn wͻ wͻn mu no “
  15,41,"Onyankopͻn kaa sε: “Woi ne kwan tenenee a εwͻ Menkyεn no “"
  15,42,"“Nokorε sε, Menkoa no deε wonni tumi wͻ wͻn so, gyesε ayerafoͻ no a wͻ’bedi w’akyi no"
  15,43,"Nokorε sε, Amanehunu gya no ne bea a yεde ahyε wͻn nyinaa bͻ"
  15,44,"(Amanehunu gya no) wͻ apono nson, na εpono no mu biara wͻ (abͻneεfoͻ) sononko a yakyekyε (ama wͻn)"